==English==

===Etymology===
From ''[[Nippon]]'', the Japanese name for Japan.

===Verb===
{{en-verb|nipponiz}}

# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To make or become [[Japanese]], as to customs, culture, or style.
# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To convert to [[katakana]] or to enable to work with the Japanese script.
# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To translate into Japanese.

